# E2E Test Orchestrator

Coordinates QE automation for the Playwright E2E suite that lives under `playwright/` in this repo. Run via `./playwright-runner.sh`.

## Intent Routing

| Intent | Command / Rule |
|--------|---------------|
| Run tests, analyze failures, fix broken tests, re-run | `/test-fix` |
| Implement E2E tests for Jira tickets | `/create-test` |
| Assess coverage gaps and generate proposals | `/coverage-analysis` |
| Compare coverage between branches (e.g. main vs release) | `/coverage-analysis --compare=<branch>` |
| Analyze coverage then implement gaps on a single branch | `/create-test --from-coverage` |
| Validate a ticket with recorded video evidence (requires playwright-cli) | `/test-and-record` |
| Explore live UI to find bugs in test-covered workflows | `/bug-hunt` |
| Write or review Playwright tests (general) | `playwright-testing.mdc` |
| QA edge case analysis | `qe-agent.mdc` |

## Ported Suite Architecture

```
Tests (.spec.ts) → import from per-folder fixture (e.g. vm-tabs-fixture.ts)
 ↓
PageObjects (playwright/src/page-objects/) → extend BasePage or PageCommons
 ↓
Clients (playwright/src/clients/) → KubernetesClient (facade), OcCliClient, VirtctlClient
```

